; Aim: take out essential TC info from wrfout_d$<domain> 
; Output:   trck.$casename.$<domain> e.g. trck.mangkhut.d01
;
; Output style (with headline): 
;   timestamp, lat, lon, minSLP, maxWS, uRadius, vRadius
